My meme

My meme was built to pay tribute to my favorite show that I tend to watch on repeat.

The Office Meme

library(magick)

# Meme Square 1 
Meme_text1 <- image_blank(width=300, height=229, color = '#000000') %>%
  image_annotate(text = "Starting a new show", color = "#999999", size = 30, font = "comfortaa", gravity = "center")

# Meme Square 2 
Bored_Micheal <- image_read("Bored Micheal.jpeg")%>% image_scale(400) 

# Meme Square 3 
Meme_text2 <- image_blank(width=300, height=283, color = '#000000') %>%
  image_annotate(text = "Rewatching
The Office
for the 18th time", color = "#999999", size = 30, font = "comfortaa", gravity = "center")

#Meme Square 4 
Happy_Micheal <- image_read("Micheal Happy.png")%>% image_scale(400)

# Creating the meme 
Bored_vector <- c(Meme_text1, Bored_Micheal)

First_row <- image_append(Bored_vector, stack = FALSE) 

Happy_vector <- c(Meme_text2, Happy_Micheal)

Second_row <- image_append(Happy_vector, stack = FALSE)

Theoffice_meme <- c(First_row, Second_row) %>%image_append(stack = TRUE)

Theoffice_meme

#Save meme

image_write(Theoffice_meme, "my_meme.png")
